Dialogs.Dialog: Do you want to stay here？ Hey, let's go.
Ah, right here. Don't pass it.
Ah, we have arrived. Time sure flies...
Okay, we've arrived. It's here, right？
It's unfortunate but we'll have to leave soon, okay？
I think this is it for today. Hehe, I still want to stay with you though.
I think we'll have to leave soon.
Yeah, let's go on a date again then.
Will this be it for today？
It's time to go home, right？
This should be it for today.
Where shall we go？ I think you should pick the location.
Okay, where do you want to go then？
Hehe. Hey, where shall we go？
Okay, have you decided where to go？
Hehe, where shall we go next？
Hehe, where shall you take me next？
No matter where we go, it's fun when we are together.
Where do we go next？ You have time to decide until I count to 3.
Is there a place you want to go？
What do you want to watch？ I want you to decide it.
Hehe, today, I'll let you choose the movie you want to watch.
What shall we watch today？ I'm fine with anything you choose.
Which one do you want to watch？
Which one do you think I want to watch？
Take your time and pick something interesting, okay？
A movie, huh？ Ah, no, I didn't mean that I don't want to watch it...
Just pick whatever you want to watch. But make sure it's an interesting one.
You know, right？ Pick a nice movie then.
Hmm... As a considerate boyfriend, I wonder if you still want to watch another movie.
Hehe, since we're here, how about watching another movie？
...Hey, how about we watch another one？
Since we're here, shall we watch another one？
What do you think？ If you don't mind, shall we watch another one？
Okay, I agree with that idea.
What shall I say...？ Hehe, just kidding.
Well... Ah, nothing. If you like it, I'm okay with it...
I see. I don't quite like it, but...
I think I'd prefer something else.
Ah, how about we have our lunch around here？
It's almost lunchtime. Shall we find something to eat？
Hehe, I'm getting hungry. Care for lunch？
It's lunchtime... What shall we do？
Hey, do you know what time it is？
I see. Shall we have lunch？
Yeah, shall we find some place to eat？
Hey, shall we stop by for some tea？
Shall we go to a coffee shop？
I'm a bit exhausted. Shall we have some tea？
When the girlfriend gets a little tired, what does the boyfriend do？
Aren't you hungry？ I think it's almost dinnertime...
That's right. Let's get something to eat.
Well, should we go to eat something now？
Are you hungry？ If you're okay, let's get something to eat somewhere.
If you're okay, how about we eat dinner somewhere？
It's about time, so why don't we go somewhere for dinner？
Ah, looks like we have arrived.
Hehe, we're here. I wonder what I'll order...
Ah, here？ Hehe. You don't have to rush like that. The shop won't run away from you.
I want to be with you longer... Is it okay？
I want to spend time with you a little longer.
Ah, you want to continue today's date, right？
Can you listen to my selfish request？
Okay, then shall we go somewhere？
Shall we go somewhere else then？
Of course. Then where shall we go？
Hmm... I want to stay with you a little longer... It's okay, right？
What should I say...？ Hehe, fine. Let's go.
I still want to visit other places.
...Hmm, you have something else to do, huh...？
Ah... Sorry, I want to go with you but I don't have time...
Hmm... It would be nice if we had more time than this, right？
Unfortunately, I don't have time. Time really flies so fast.
Hmm... What if I can't go with you...？
Hmm... I'll have to pass. Maybe next time, okay？
Sorry, I think we shouldn't go there today.
